WEBVTT

1
00:12:34.500 --> 00:12:37.660 
如果他们走前门  咱们就从后门撤
If they come in that door, we go out this door.

2
00:12:37.660 --> 00:12:40.060 
如果他们从后门来  栗宝  你就挡住他们
If they come in that door, Chestnut, you block them,

3
00:12:40.060 --> 00:12:42.530 
南茜  你就去抓瞎他们
and, Nancy, you go for their eyes.

4
00:12:44.980 --> 00:12:46.770 
算了  大难临头各自飞吧
You know what? Let's just say our good-byes now.

5
00:12:46.770 --> 00:12:48.500 
快烧开  快烧开啊
Boil, boil, boil.

6
00:12:49.140 --> 00:12:50.670 
没时间了
No time!

7
00:12:50.670 --> 00:12:56.490 
门外的人  我手上有锅很烫的水
Whoever you are, I have a pot of pretty hot water!

8
00:13:01.780 --> 00:13:03.730 
这堆玩意是怎么回事
What is all this junk?

